OL,3,CD-Day veteran looks set to receive
OL,4,Chonour of freedom of Derbyshire
OL,6,FDerbyshire D-Day veteran Albert Keir
OL,7,Flooks set to be honoured with the
OL,8,FFreedom of Derbyshire.
OL,10,FAt a meeting of Derbyshire County
OL,11,FCouncil's full council on 27 November,
OL,12,Fcouncillors voted unanimously to agree
OL,13,Fin principle to bestow the honour of
OL,14,FFreedom of the County of Derbyshire to
OL,15,FMr Keir.
OL,17,FIt's in recognition of his
OL,18,Fachievements during his life and
OL,19,Fcareer, including the part he played
OL,20,Fin the Second World War.
