OL,4,Chonour of freedom of Derbyshire
OL,6,FFollowing the agreement in principle,
OL,7,Fthe formality of agreeing to confer
OL,8,Fthe title will be made at a special
OL,9,Fmeeting of the full council on a date
OL,10,Fto be set next year where Mr Keir will
OL,11,Fbe invited to receive the honour.
OL,13,FMr Keir said: "I was very pleasantly
OL,14,Fsurprised and thrilled to be
OL,15,Fconsidered for such an honour and
OL,16,Fwould be extremely proud to accept it.
OL,18,F"I would like to thank everybody
OL,19,Finvolved in the process and for
OL,20,Fputting my name forward."
