OL,6,FDerbyshire County Council Civic
OL,7,FChairman Councillor Tony Kemp said:
OL,8,F"We are delighted that our council was
OL,9,Funanimous in its decision to agree in
OL,10,Fprinciple to the bestowing of the
OL,11,Fhonour of the Freedom of the County of
OL,12,FDerbyshire to Mr Keir.
OL,14,F"He is an extraordinary man and one of
OL,15,Fthe last surviving veterans of D-Day.
OL,17,F"We very much look forward to
OL,18,Fofficially bestowing the honour on him
OL,19,Ffollowing a formal, final agreement at
OL,20,Fa special meeting of our full council
OL,21,Fnext year."
